{"tid":2223532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩抗爭港人獲美政治庇護   八九民運領袖：證港人權狀況嚴重惡化","createTime":"2020-09-30T02:11:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T03:33:57.000Z","uid":188515,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"79830f5af0dad3751f5558f6f693fa99f94fa21b","tid":2223532,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:11:41.000Z","msg":"香港人超過一年的反送中抗爭，無數人除了被捕外，更有人被迫離開家園。移居美國洛杉磯的八九民運學生領袖鄭存柱向《蘋果》獨家透露，從美國移民局官方得到最新信息，兩名來自香港的年輕人，正式獲得美國政府給予政治庇護。<br />\n<br />\n在美國洛杉磯律師行擔任移民顧問工作的鄭存柱表示，該兩名曾參加香港反送中抗議活動的年輕人在年初到了美國，惟因為武漢肺炎疫情，移民局一度關門，到了6月才恢復辦工，他們提交庇護申請，8月當局安排面談。移民局於當地時間29日公佈兩人獲取美國政治的政治庇護。<br />\n<br />\n鄭存柱指，兩名港人去年曾多次參與本港反送中示威，後來逃往美國，「他們到美國後，並沒有停下來，繼續參與當地聲援香港的活動。」而得悉消息後，二人都感到非常欣喜。<br />\n<br />\n鄭存主認為，二人政治庇護獲批，證明香港人權狀況在過去的一年有嚴重的惡化。原先的香港，擁有民主自由和司法獨立。香港人鮮提出申請政治庇護，而西方民主國家也很難批准香港人的庇護申請。但是自2019年反送中以來，香港警察的暴力鎮壓、通過港區國安法等等，都表明中國徹底摒棄了對香港人「一國兩制」的承諾。而美國也不再認可香港是一個可以保有民主法制的獨立地區。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200930/LJFBQ5F3PVC7XPDRR3OQSHAGDE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200930%2FLJFBQ5F3PVC7XPDRR3OQSHAGDE%2F&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWNg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=eb338acd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200930%2FLJFBQ5F3PVC7XPDRR3OQSHAGDE%2F&h=b3ddceb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200930/LJFBQ5F3PVC7XPDRR3OQSHAGDE/</a>"},{"pid":"45c211dd25d6d63922f7c6099d5338221d9b680d","tid":2223532,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:13:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a38f7ea93e97fbe3286b93cdd2ca63f36ae0ce8","tid":2223532,"uid":53592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10b73d8082f9c16985c37e0348a160c879f4b43","tid":2223532,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e945d5167785a0561cea2bc4c38e7c3af2314c46","tid":2223532,"uid":303110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:16:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d97187d9f53263bc9b62fe61ac06ad4620e4c4","tid":2223532,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:18:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062c045fc4fcc2eb4a2f54c7b7e837a7cc702ae4","tid":2223532,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:56:08.000Z","msg":"好消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3f705f7d02489638411c86a832a3096be904e4","tid":2223532,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T03:00:20.000Z","msg":"又諗起台灣個兩個on9"},{"pid":"ac3f2a315017e541150da70c571c6350dbc2e6ac","tid":2223532,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T03:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794303a13b514de46a1d018af6086ffb1e807750","tid":2223532,"uid":263349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T03:33:57.000Z","msg":"之前係咩人 一直叫人去台灣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}